title: Coronavirus update: Flight home for Aussies stranded in Cambodia in 'advanced stages'
description: Australia's embassy in Cambodia is in the advanced stages of organising a flight home for the more than 500 Australian citizens stranded there during the coronavirus pandemic.
content:
Posted 
April 08, 2020 02:48:51
Australia's embassy in Cambodia is in the advanced stages of organising a flight home for Australians stranded there, while in the UK the Queen sends a message of support to Prime Minister Boris Johnson's family.
